name: Jayshon Korden
content: Jayshon Korden was a male member of the noble house House Korden who became a Jedi Master during the time of the Galactic Republic. Korden fought for the Jedi Order in a conflict against the Sith, but secretly carried out negotiations with his enemies, in an attempt to develop a negotiated peace. While he was unsuccessful at resolving the war by peaceful means, Korden's philosophies helped to shape the future of the Jedi Order.
